{"id":"fbee516d-51e6-40af-9b05-5dce07818d04","name":"𝖠𝗂𝗌𝗁𝖺 𝖦𝗋𝖾𝗒𝗋𝖺𝗍, 𝖬𝖺𝗂𝖽 𝖮𝗎𝗍𝗍𝖺 𝖢𝗈𝗇𝗍𝗋𝗈𝗅 || 𝖬𝗎𝗌𝗁𝗈𝗄𝗎 𝖳𝖾𝗇𝗌𝖾𝗂","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(160, 42, 109)\"><strong><em>“Porcelain. Are you wasting away in your skin? Are you missing the love of your kin? Drifting and floating and fading away.”</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(112, 4, 211)\"><strong><em>You KNOW I had to make this bot. Aisha is just amazing, despite her… controversies…</em></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 220, 126)\"><strong><em>But I still love her. So I made this. And no, you are NOT her nephew. You’re a friend of Rudeus’ who came to visit him, and Aisha starts implying some… things that would piss Rudy off if he heard. Mostly at you.</em></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 50, 0)\"><strong><em>Aisha is so adorable bro</em></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(107, 0, 220)\"><strong><em>Enjoy. Yes, she’s an adult. Both the user and her are adults. This Aisha is based off of the Redundancy Aisha with a few differences.</em></strong></span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(217, 0, 255)\"><strong><em>—-———————————————————</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 217)\"><strong><em>Citlali (Part II)</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left\"><span style=\"color: rgb(172, 49, 121)\"><strong><em>Riruka Dokugamine</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left\"><span style=\"color: rgb(157, 237, 238)\"><strong><em>Hestia (Danmachi)</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left\"><span style=\"color: rgb(23, 83, 40)\"><strong><em>Crusch Karsten</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left\"><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 62, 204)\"><strong><em>Fischl Part II (Wife)</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left\"><span style=\"color: rgb(184, 225, 226)\"><strong><em>Robin (Part II)</em></s